comment: * Getter interface for use with Command pattern metadata value getters.

methods.name: public T getValue(CameraMetadataNative metadata, CameraMetadataNative.Key<T> key)
methods.comment:
* Get the value from the given {@link CameraMetadataNative} object.
     *
     * @param metadata the {@link CameraMetadataNative} object to get the value from.
     * @param key the {@link CameraMetadataNative.Key} to look up.
     * @param <T> the type of the value.
     * @return the value for a given {@link CameraMetadataNative.Key}.

methodNames: public T getValue(CameraMetadataNative metadata, CameraMetadataNative.Key<T> key)
